      "role": "user",
      "content": "it’s more than just resting though. it’s like... the vessel is still here, but the thing that made the vessel worth having is gone. i look in the mirror and i just see a container for nothing. a shell with no life in it. does it even make sense to keep the shell around if there's nothing inside to carry?",
